| Sort events by date/time  | SearchFilter             |
| Fetch event details       |                          |
| Provide event lists       |                          |
| Return filtered/searched  |                          |
| event data                |                          |
| Handle missing/unavailable|                          |
| event data gracefully     |                          |
+---------------------------+--------------------------+


